41:14.264 --> 41:15.849
from under the tables.

41:15.932 --> 41:17.434
Yeah. Yummy.

41:17.517 --> 41:19.895
Is this a reprimand?

41:19.978 --> 41:20.979
No.

41:21.062 --> 41:22.731
I'm a fun person.

41:22.814 --> 41:25.358
I like to have fun. So...

41:25.442 --> 41:28.236
whoever can correctly guess
how many pieces of chewing gum

41:28.320 --> 41:32.365
are in this jar wins a 12-pack.

41:32.449 --> 41:34.242
We will pass the jar around.

41:34.326 --> 41:35.452
You can write down your guesses

41:35.535 --> 41:37.287
and hand 'em in to your server.

41:40.957 --> 41:43.335
An 11-pack.

41:47.756 --> 41:49.508
<i>♪♪ Thought you could
take control ♪♪</i>

41:49.591 --> 41:51.134
<i>♪♪ Betrayin' players all ♪♪</i>

41:51.218 --> 41:54.429
